    <hr class="story">
    <div class="left">
        <p>The crowd showed up! And we were so thankful for all the support that we received at the event and even beyond. 
            We raised a total of about 50,000 KES during the event.</p>
        <p>
            The actual work then had to get going. 
            After expenses related to the event venue, equipment and compensating the performers for travel, 
            we directed all the remaining funds, about 30,000 towards construction of shelves. 
            Denue led this effort in making sure that the shelves were constructed at the school library. 
            And in August, we paid one more visit to the school to shelve the books and launch the library. 
        </p>
    </div>
