    <hr class="story">

    <div>
        <p>There was still much left to do after August. 
            The library needed seats and chairs and a working lending system. And - of course - an official launching with the students and teachers. 
            The project was later picked up by Safaricom.
        <br>
            We couldn't have done all that we did without the support of every single person who believed in us, 
            who contributed a book or two, who attended the concert, 
            who listened to us talk about an idea that at some points seemed very far off from becoming a reality. 
            We really do appreciate you all.
        </p>
